title: Obé Fitness Nabs Backing from Samsung, Athleta
itunes:title: Obé Fitness Nabs Backing from Samsung, Athleta
description:
Mark Mullett and Ashley Mills, Co-Founders of Obé, discuss new funding from Samsung Next, Athleta, WW International and more for the digital-workout platform.

Host: Tim Stenovec. Producer: Paul Brennan.
